++ Use References You Can See

URYCS means that if you see a reference to some information then you can use it. This is an example of HelpTheUser.

++Examples

    * A file path is technically a reference to a particular a particular point in a tree. Each branch represents a folder and is represented on the screen by its name. It should be possible to interact with each branch individually as if it were a full path. Considering that each branch is also a container for files, it should be possible to GetInto these folders and subsequent files.
    * This is to Open File Neighbours

